;個D係咩先喇<br />\n依家宮內廳指定個堆除左戰國之後個堆可以確定真係個個天皇既山墳之外<br />\n其他入面訓緊個個係咪真係天皇都真係幾撚有疑問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁兵馬俑都唔知有冇泰皇<br />\n曹操墓嗰個係唔係真係曹操啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算冇瞓入去,本身古蹟都係有佢意義<br />\n除非你話我知根本連古蹟都唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284d83b9c7a05952c0ec36591a1a4c7d3c8d1f5a","tid":874081,"uid":38546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:29:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://culture.people.com.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fculture.people.com.cn&d=0%2BfN0%2FGWhSQDVPNeac0z7P1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=37a1db84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">culture.people.com.cn</a> : 你也是中國人。"},{"pid":"6d1398a63cc5008e35560a8d6df4f69634d423eb","tid":874081,"uid":61660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1672dedf3293d1fc2027a5bfe684485e4a3cbe4a","tid":874081,"uid":52881,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b82599f0a375a44bf130c4337adcb185105ac055","tid":874081,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e34631d3e71115c9b83916442d8bc3556285ef6","tid":874081,"uid":52881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"相對嘅姐<br />\n比起來日本叫留低好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:15:09.000Z","msg":"咁你要睇下&quot;留低&quot;個D係咩先喇<br />\n依家宮內廳指定個堆除左戰國之後個堆可以確定真係個個天皇既山墳之外<br />\n其他入面訓緊個個係咪真係天皇都真係幾撚有疑問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁兵馬俑都唔知有冇泰皇<br />\n曹操墓嗰個係唔係真係曹操啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算冇瞓入去,本身古蹟都係有佢意義<br />\n除非你話我知根本連古蹟都唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"老實講真係好多可能係咩都唔知架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔少宮內廳指定話係個D俾日本仔自己D考古話唔係架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本D天皇陵維護係明治時期先開始重視架咋<br />\n江戶時代叫有少少<br />\n但之前D人斬撚左天皇墳頭D樹去燒係上面耕田都唔少啊<br />\n係廟個D都仲叫好少少但唔少又係連間廟一齊荒廢埋<br />\n所以實際上唔只入面仲有冇天皇（天皇遺骸俾人盗出黎唔係未試過）<br />\n好多連係咪天皇陸其實都真係有疑問<br />\n<br />\n而你講開秦始皇陵<br />\n佢唔係未俾人盗過只係冇人盗到入地宮入面<br />\n好多年前做過一次探測<br />\n係話佢入面D泥係冇俾人攪過既<br />\n所以其實應該就未俾人郁過"},{"pid":"53a062cd67f6ed1090e86a0b02127d6666adbf47","tid":874081,"uid":176910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:44:18.000Z","msg":"留名睇中國人又係度認親認戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抗日戰爭變內戰指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef84883f1924948957167875aaf5e60b23076ed","tid":874081,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:44:21.000Z","msg":"有條河既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc6d65b6b9883168dc7b798029a02c92fd0d0fc","tid":874081,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53a062cd67f6ed1090e86a0b02127d6666adbf47","tid":874081,"uid":176910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:44:18.000Z","msg":"留名睇中國人又係度認親認戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抗日戰爭變內戰指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"當時係中國內戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2124a6b245225f9588bacc913ed923210fef25","tid":874081,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:24:20.000Z","msg":"第一幅係集合哂確認